nnotation whose callout was tapped."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"annotation"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This method is called when the user taps on the body of the callout view, as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"opposed to the callout’s left or right accessory view. If the annotation has a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"custom callout view via the "},{"code":"-mapView:calloutViewForAnnotation:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" method, this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method is only called whenever the callout view calls its delegate’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNCalloutViewDelegate\/calloutViewTapped:","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" method."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If this method is present on the delegate, the standard callout view’s body","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"momentarily highlights when the user taps it, whether or not this method does","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"anything in response to the tap.","type":"text"}]},{"anchor":"Related-examples","type":"heading","level":4,"text":"Related examples"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"TODO: Display custom views as callouts, learn how to trigger an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"action when an "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":"s "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" is tapped."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:tapOnCalloutForAnnotation:"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:taponcalloutforannotation:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapViewDelegate","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol defines a set of optional methods that you","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"can use to receive map-related update messages. Because many map operations","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"require the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","type":"reference"},{"text":" class to load data asynchronously, the map view calls","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"these methods to notify your application when specific operations complete. The","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"map view also uses these methods to request information about annotations","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"displayed on the map, such as the styles and interaction modes to apply to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"individual annotations.","type":"text"}],"title":"MLNMapViewDelegate"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"title":"MLNAnnotation","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate/mapView:tapOnCalloutForAnnotation:":{"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:tapOnCalloutForAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:taponcalloutforannotation:","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Tells the delegate that the user tapped on an annotation’s callout view.","type":"text"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"mapView:tapOnCalloutForAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"mapView:tapOnCalloutForAnnotation:","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:tapOnCalloutForAnnotation:","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNCalloutViewDelegate/calloutViewTapped:":{"url":"\/documentation\/ma